  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In order to evaluate the implementation for the recommendations about the patient care for
      atrial fibrillation in aged patients, a non-interventional study is performed retrospectively
      by comparing two approach of the focus in Cardiology Department and in Geriatric unit.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
